Navigate narrow airplane or train aisles with ease with Werks Traveler™ 4.0. The new dual-caster construction allows for 360°, zero weight-in-hand maneuverability. Lighter. Easier. Better Than Ever. The most popular collection of Victorinox Travel Gear, Werks Traveler™ 4.0 is now better than ever with dual-caster uprights to accommodate the needs of today's traveler. From the makers of the original Swiss Army Knife.
